replies.body:
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 

We'd play what we enjoyed, and ban what you don't want to play against or key cornerstone champions for certain team comps. 

However, that's even assuming that you're playing draft to begin with, despite blind pick being the much more played game type... and call me crazy, but i'd much rather have a chance of winning or losing any game based on how well i play, not on the average power of each team.
